data.description: Welcome home to this 4BR 2.5BA home in Fieldstone Estates. This home features an additional parking pad in the driveway, and a game day patio with a fireplace out back! On the main level there is a grand two story foyer, formal living room that could be a home office, separate dining room and a kitchen that is open to the family room. The kitchen has granite counters, stainless appliances and a large pantry. Upstairs are all the bedrooms and laundry. The primary suite is oversized with plenty of space in the bedroom and bathroom! Enjoy the outdoor space in this home with the extended covered patio and outdoor fireplace looking over a large flat yard.
